QuestData.Title: Fiends from the Netherworld
QuestData.Description: Those ogre magi inside the Undershell have summoned defenders: fleshling fiends from the netherworld.$B$BI do not want to see these aberrations used against our forces. While you are in there, destroy all of them!
QuestData.CompletionText: Not all of the fiends have been destroyed.
QuestData.RewardText: That's one less thing we need to think about during the final assault.
